S.FORM: Yoweri Museveni I 1944 a miheca saka 9 folad saka 15 a romi'ad masofoc ci Yoweri Museveni, malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Uganda anini i ci Yoweri Museveni, patirengan a romi'ad i 1986 a miheca saka 1 folad saka 29 a romi'ad.
